          <td class="paramname"><code></code></td><td>)</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody></table>
</div><div class="memdoc">
<p>Get the reset reason without verifying it.</p>
<dl class="section return"><dt>Returns</dt><dd>The reset reason </dd></dl>

</div>
</div>
<a class="anchor" id="gac99cc83ea966538c41d526d3cae8eba7"></a>
<div class="memitem">
<div class="memproto">
      <table class="memname">
        <tbody><tr>
          <td class="memname">void reset_invalidateResetReason </td>
          <td>(</td>
          <td class="paramtype">void&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="paramname"><code></code></td><td>)</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody></table>
</div><div class="memdoc">
<p>Invalidate the reset reason.</p>
<dl class="section note"><dt>Note</dt><dd>This will also disable the reset counter if it is in use. </dd></dl>

</div>
</div>
<a class="anchor" id="ga88d3135fb4c98707e0b2547b3ceb7075"></a>
<div class="memitem">
<div class="memproto">
      <table class="memname">
        <tbody><tr>
