</div><div class="memdoc">
<p>Classify reset and get the reset reason.</p>
<dl class="section return"><dt>Returns</dt><dd>Reset cause or <a href="group-ResetInterface#gabd9584cf55d7474c4068ba007f9f6f96" class="el" >BOOTLOADER_RESET_REASON_UNKNOWN</a> </dd></dl>

